#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.254"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.254:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.254:0.2"
msgid "26. Abhiññāvagga"
msgstr "26. Insight"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.254:0.3"
msgid "254. Abhiññāsutta"
msgstr "254. Insight"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.247"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.254:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, bhikkhave, dhammā."
msgstr "Mendicants, there are these four things."

msgctxt "an4.254:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.254:1.3"
msgid "Atthi, bhikkhave, dhammā abhiññā pariññeyyā;"
msgstr ""
"There are things that should be completely understood by direct knowledge."

msgctxt "an4.254:1.4"
msgid "atthi, bhikkhave, dhammā abhiññā pahātabbā;"
msgstr "There are things that should be given up by direct knowledge."

msgctxt "an4.254:1.5"
msgid "atthi, bhikkhave, dhammā abhiññā bhāvetabbā;"
msgstr "There are things that should be developed by direct knowledge."

msgctxt "an4.254:1.6"
msgid "atthi, bhikkhave, dhammā abhiññā sacchikātabbā."
msgstr "There are things that should be realized by direct knowledge."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.254:2.1"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, dhammā abhiññā pariññeyyā?"
msgstr ""
"And what are the things that should be completely understood by direct "
"knowledge?"

#. VAR: Pañcupādānakkhandhā → pañcupādānakkhandhātissa vacanīyaṃ (mr)
msgctxt "an4.254:2.2"
msgid "Pañcupādānakkhandhā—"
msgstr "The five grasping aggregates."

msgctxt "an4.254:2.3"
msgid "ime vuccanti, bhikkhave, dhammā abhiññā pariññeyyā."
msgstr ""
"These are called the things that should be completely understood by direct "
"knowledge."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.254:3.1"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, dhammā abhiññā pahātabbā?"
msgstr "And what are the things that should be given up by direct knowledge?"

msgctxt "an4.254:3.2"
msgid "Avijjā ca bhavataṇhā ca—"
msgstr "Ignorance and craving for continued existence."

msgctxt "an4.254:3.3"
msgid "ime vuccanti, bhikkhave, dhammā abhiññā pahātabbā."
msgstr ""
"These are called the things that should be given up by direct knowledge."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.254:4.1"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, dhammā abhiññā bhāvetabbā?"
msgstr "And what are the things that should be developed by direct knowledge?"

msgctxt "an4.254:4.2"
msgid "Samatho ca vipassanā ca—"
msgstr "Serenity and discernment."

msgctxt "an4.254:4.3"
msgid "ime vuccanti, bhikkhave, dhammā abhiññā bhāvetabbā."
msgstr ""
"These are called the things that should be developed by direct knowledge."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an4.254:5.1"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, dhammā abhiññā sacchikātabbā?"
msgstr "And what are the things that should be realized by direct knowledge?"

msgctxt "an4.254:5.2"
msgid "Vijjā ca vimutti ca—"
msgstr "Knowledge and freedom."

msgctxt "an4.254:5.3"
msgid "ime vuccanti, bhikkhave, dhammā abhiññā sacchikātabbā."
msgstr ""
"These are called the things that should be realized by direct knowledge."

msgctxt "an4.254:5.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro dhammā”ti."
msgstr "These are the four things.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.254:5.5"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
